{#**
 * 场景提示词基础模板
 * 格式参考: video-prompt-templates.md v2.0
 *#}
{% block HEADER %}
RAW landscape photo, cinematic {{ shot_type }} shot, shot on ARRI Alexa, 35mm anamorphic lens, 8k resolution,
{% endblock %}

{% block LOCATION %}
location: {{ location }},
{% endblock %}

{% block ENVIRONMENT %}
environment details:
{% for env in environment %}
- {{ env }},
{% endfor %}
{% endblock %}

{% block MAIN_SUBJECT %}
the {{ subject_type }}: {{ main_subject }},
{% endblock %}

{% block LIGHTING %}
lighting & atmosphere:
{% for light in lighting %}
- {{ light }},
{% endfor %}
{% endblock %}

{% block COMPOSITION %}
composition: {{ composition }},
{% endblock %}

{% block TECHNICAL %}
technical: high dynamic range, film grain, {{ atmosphere }} atmosphere, photorealistic textures
{% endblock %}

{% block NEGATIVE %}
negative: {{ negative_prompt }}
{% endblock %}
